<subSubSection id="C32F39DC95514C67FF22FCD2FB8FFC43" pageId="2" pageNumber="145" type="description">
<paragraph id="8B8A6A5795514C67FF22FCD2FB12FC63" blockId="2.[166,1225,751,938]" pageId="2" pageNumber="145">
E t y m o l o g y. From Latin — Plana = flat; from Greek micro — short, small; “semenovi” in honour of 
<collectorName id="26C00F8195514C67FEABFCF2FDA6FCA3" box="[338,575,815,842]" pageId="2" pageNumber="145">Dr. Yuriy Semenov</collectorName>
(
<collectingCounty id="62EB12DB95514C67FDAAFCEDFC14FCA0" box="[595,909,815,842]" pageId="2" pageNumber="145">Palaeontological Museum</collectingCounty>
of the 
<collectingMunicipality id="6BEEF02D95514C67FC14FCEDFE15FC83" pageId="2" pageNumber="145">National Museum of Natural History</collectingMunicipality>
, 
<location id="8EEA3C8C95514C67FE62FC8DFC94FC83" LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:039CDB4195514C67FF5FFD0DFB8FFC43:8EEA3C8C95514C67FE62FC8DFC94FC83" box="[411,781,847,873]" country="Ukraine" county="Palaeontological Museum" municipality="National Museum of Natural History" name="National Academy of Sciences" pageId="2" pageNumber="145" stateProvince="Kyiv">National Academy of Sciences</location>
of 
<collectingCountry id="F3222AC795514C67FCC4FC8DFC39FC83" box="[829,928,847,873]" name="Ukraine" pageId="2" pageNumber="145">Ukraine</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingRegion id="49F1A4B595514C67FC56FC8DFC7FFC83" box="[943,998,847,873]" country="Ukraine" name="Kyiv" pageId="2" pageNumber="145">Kyiv</collectingRegion>
= 
<collectionCode id="ED24F29295514C67FBF7FC92FB04FC80" box="[1038,1181,848,874]" pageId="2" pageNumber="145">NMNHU-P</collectionCode>
) in recognition of his contributions to the discovery and collecting of this fossil material.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B8A6A5795514C67FF22FC52FB8FFC43" blockId="2.[166,1225,751,938]" box="[219,1046,911,938]" pageId="2" pageNumber="145">
